e LinkedServer "' + S.name + '" is configured to work with IP address. On DR based IP This will not work automaticly.' Message, NULL URL, 'Worning' Severity, 'Change data_source on "' + S.name + '" from IP(' + S.data_source + ') to Name DNS based' Action FROM Client.Servers S WHERE [Utility].[ufn_Util_clr_RegexIsMatch] (data_source,'^\d*\.\d*\.\d*\.\d*') = 1 AND S.guid = @Guid AND S.is_linked = 1;
